<!DOCTYPE html>
<!--
  `nl-studio` opts this window into the light theme (see styles.css): the same
  stylesheet is bundled into the game runtime, which must stay dark regardless
  of the player's OS, so only windows showing Studio chrome carry the class.
  Set per-app by renderHtml in project/build/utils.js — Dev Mode hosts the game
  itself and is deliberately left without it.
-->
